00:08:28.819 --> 00:08:35.379
Our loving Heavenly Father especially watches over all who endeavour to do His will,

00:08:35.940 --> 00:08:42.259
but in all of His mercy He also draws humble people who may not yet know Him.

00:08:43.620 --> 00:08:49.940
How many of us were in dire straits only to be introduced to the truth and to get to know

00:08:49.940 --> 00:08:58.100
Jehovah at the right time? That was no coincidence. That's a consequence of Jehovah's love,

00:08:58.899 --> 00:09:02.419
and His desire to give people comfort through the hope He provides.

00:09:05.450 --> 00:09:11.129
